@startuml EpisodeReplayBuffer_Class
!theme plain

title EpisodeReplayBuffer 继承体系

package "RLlib" {

    class ReplayBufferInterface {
        {abstract} +__len__() : int
        {abstract} +add(batch)
        {abstract} +sample(num_items) : Any
        {abstract} +get_state() : Dict
        {abstract} +set_state(state)
    }

    class EpisodeReplayBuffer {
        +capacity : int
        +batch_size_B : int
        +batch_length_T : int
        +episodes : deque
        +episode_id_to_index : dict
        +_indices : list
        +_num_episodes_evicted : int
        +_num_timesteps : int
        +_num_timesteps_added : int
        +sampled_timesteps : int
        +rng : np.random.Generator
        +metrics : MetricsLogger
        --
        +add(episodes)
        +_sample_batch() : dict
        +_sample_episodes() : list
        +sample(...) : Any
        +get_num_episodes() : int
        +get_num_timesteps() : int
        +get_sampled_timesteps() : int
        +get_added_timesteps() : int
        +get_state() : Dict
        +set_state(state)
        +_update_add_metrics()
        +_update_sample_metrics()
    }

    ReplayBufferInterface <|-- EpisodeReplayBuffer
}

note top of ReplayBufferInterface
抽象接口，RLlib 定义
end note

note bottom of EpisodeReplayBuffer
核心：以 episode 为原子单位存储在 deque 中
扁平 _indices 列表支持 O(1) 均匀随机采样
end note

@enduml
